itunes:title: 335. Andy, Malik Deshawn & DJ CTI: Favorite Big Booty Latina, Iran May Try To Assassinate Trump & Giant Marijuana Cloud
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ are joined in the studio by castrologist Malik Deshawn. They discuss AOC being trolled by Alex Stein on her way to the Capitol building, the US intelligence report that warned of a possible assassination attempt on Trump, and the Colombian police burning 1.5 tons of seized drugs resulting in a giant marijuana cloud over the town.
